      "content": "yo what's the consensus on the best end-game build for Stormcaller right now?",
      "author": { "id": "900000000000000001", "name": "kael", "nickname": "Kael" }
    },
    {
      "id": "1000000000000000002",
      "type": "Default",
      "timestamp": "2024-03-12T18:01:30.000+00:00",
      "content": "crit build is still king at end-game. you stack Shattered Prism (crit chance) + Tempest Core for the multiplier",
      "author": { "id": "900000000000000002", "name": "vyn", "nickname": "Vyntra" },
      "reference": { "messageId": "1000000000000000001" }
    },
    {
      "id": "1000000000000000003",
      "type": "Default",
      "timestamp": "2024-03-12T18:02:10.000+00:00",
      "content": "specifically you want 65% crit chance before diminishing returns kick in, then everything goes into crit damage",
      "author": { "id": "900000000000000002", "name": "vyn", "nickname": "Vyntra" }
    },
    {
      "id": "1000000000000000004",
      "type": "Default",
      "timestamp": "2024-03-12T18:03:45.000+00:00",
      "content": "don't forget the Stormweave set bonus (4pc) — it converts 20% of crit damage into AoE. mandatory for clearing the Sunken Vault",
      "author": { "id": "900000000000000003", "name": "mira", "nickname": "Mirae" }
    },
    {
      "id": "1000000000000000005",
      "type": "Default",
      "timestamp": "2024-03-12T18:05:00.000+00:00",
      "content": "isn't mana build better for boss sustain though?",
