    },
    {
      "id": "1000000000000000007",
      "type": "Default",
      "timestamp": "2024-03-12T18:07:55.000+00:00",
      "content": "tl;dr best Stormcaller end-game build = crit (Shattered Prism + Tempest Core + Stormweave 4pc), aim 65% crit then crit dmg. Mana build is dead post-2.3.",
